RESURRECT - Return from death
=============================

Usage: resurrect

When you die, you are sent to the Netherworld. Use this command to return
to the world of the living. This command only works in the Netherworld.

Effects:
  - Teleports you to the Town Square
  - Your HP is already restored to full
  - Your character is automatically saved

After resurrection, go back to where you died to recover your items from
your corpse!

Note: Player corpses last 1 hour. Monster corpses last 5 minutes.

See also: help death, help corpses
